    <item>
      <title>马萨诸塞州州长希望拜登考虑退出竞选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/massachusetts-governor-wants-biden-to-weigh-dropping-out-of-race</link>
      <description><![CDATA[几天前，白宫与其他民主党州领导人一起寻求马萨诸塞州州长莫拉·希利 (Maura Healey) 的支持，马萨诸塞州州长莫拉·希利敦促总统乔·拜登考虑是否继续竞选连任。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/massachusetts-governor-wants-biden-to-weigh-dropping-out-of-race</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 19:35:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哨兵洲际弹道导弹成本再次飙升至每枚 2.14 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/cost-of-new-icbm-swells-again-in-fresh-embarrassment-to-pentagon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国空军新型“哨兵”洲际导弹的成本预测再次上升，目前预计该计划将花费纳税人 1410 亿美元，比四年前的预测高出 81%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/cost-of-new-icbm-swells-again-in-fresh-embarrassment-to-pentagon</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 19:33:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普希望在豁免裁决后暂停秘密记录案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/trump-wants-florida-documents-case-paused-after-supreme-court-ruling</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院裁定前总统唐纳德·特朗普可能免于与官方行为相关的刑事指控，之后他要求暂停因涉嫌不当处理机密信息而进行的起诉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/trump-wants-florida-documents-case-paused-after-supreme-court-ruling</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 18:30:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈马斯放弃停火反对意见，谈判将继续进行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/mediators-set-to-continue-gaza-truce-talks-after-latest-round</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位知情人士称，哈马斯已经放弃反对美国支持的旨在停止加沙与以色列冲突的停火提议，这是迄今为止最明显的迹象，表明经过数月无果而终的谈判后，停火是有可能的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/mediators-set-to-continue-gaza-truce-talks-after-latest-round</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 18:12:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>7 月 4 日暴力事件导致全国至少 33 人死亡，数十人受伤</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-07-05/shootings-on-july-fourth-leave-14-injured-in-chicago-1-dead-in-philadelphia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当局称，七月四日长周末期间发生的枪击和其他暴力事件已造成至少 33 人死亡，其中包括芝加哥的 11 人，全国各地还有数十人受伤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-07-05/shootings-on-july-fourth-leave-14-injured-in-chicago-1-dead-in-philadelphia</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 14:30:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>保守党混乱统治后，斯塔默誓言保持稳定和温和</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/starmer-vows-stability-and-moderation-in-reset-for-uk-politics</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国新任首相基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 率领工党在选举中取得压倒性胜利，结束了保守党 14 年动荡内讧的统治，承诺组建一个“稳定与温和”的政府。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/starmer-vows-stability-and-moderation-in-reset-for-uk-politics</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 12:14:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登坚持立场，宣布继续参加总统竞选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/biden-heads-into-make-or-break-weekend-for-2024-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登在访问摇摆州威斯康星州期间宣布他将继续参加总统竞选，并谴责将他赶下台的行为，并展开激烈努力以恢复对他是否适合担任公职深表怀疑的选民、捐助者和党内官员的信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/biden-heads-into-make-or-break-weekend-for-2024-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 02:33:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
